    <h1>Returns, Refunds & Cancellations</h1>
    <h6>How do I return my order?</h6>
    <p>If something isn’t right or you have simply changed your mind, please contact us and we will start your returns process, subject to our returns policy and conditions. Please note do not allow prescription medication to be returned. This is because of safety concern reasons and we are not authorised to resell the medication. You can bring any unneeded or expired medication to your local pharmacy, and they will safely dispose of it.</p>
