    <p>If you have returned the goods to us under this consumer right of return and refund pursuant to the Regulations because they are faulty or misdescribed, we will refund the price of the goods in full, together with any applicable delivery charges, and any reasonable costs you incur in returning the item to us.</p>
    <p>We will refund you on the credit card, or debit card used by you to pay, but in the event of a partial refund, we reserve the right to issue a cheque to you. If the card you used to pay with expires before the refund is made please call us to give us your new card details.</p>
    <p>If goods have been delivered to you before you decide to cancel your contract:</p>
